================
Pre-requisites : 
================

Following packages needs to be installed:
1. python2.7+,  
2. requests_oauthlib library, 
3. requests library
4. firefox
5. pyvirtualdisplay
6. selenium

To install python
#apt-get install python

To install requests_oauthlib and requests library
#pip install requests_oauthlib requests

To install firefox on ubuntu 12
#sudo add-apt-repository ppa:ubuntu-mozilla-daily/ppa && sudo apt-get update
#sudo apt-get install firefox-trunk
#firefox &

For display :
#sudo apt-get install xvfb
#pip install pyvirtualdisplay

For selenium:
#pip install selenium

================
How to execute : 
================

1. Execute the script with the following command: 
	#python main.py -i <instance_name>
2. <instance_name> could be production or staging 
3. The automation script starts executing all apis and its endpoints.

Note : credentials are store in ConfigFileProduction.py for production instance and in ConfigFileStaging.py for staging instance. You can change it according to your requirement.
